01:05.300 --> 01:07.567
Man, I can't wait
to be married.

01:07.684 --> 01:10.400
All right, fine.
Look, we could talk all day,

01:10.434 --> 01:16.201
but I see one little fella that
still needs your attention.

01:17.417 --> 01:19.534
We still have schotzie?

01:19.975 --> 01:21.508
I thought he ran away.

01:21.542 --> 01:24.409
No, he's been hiding
underneath the house.

01:24.875 --> 01:26.242
