01:32.389 --> 01:37.389
Look, mom, maybe you should stop worrying about
everyone else so much and start thinking about yourself.

01:37.423 --> 01:40.156
Maybe you should find something
to enrich your life.

01:40.239 --> 01:41.789
Oh, may I suggest

01:41.839 --> 01:44.172
the teachings of the jedi?

01:45.922 --> 01:49.906
And may I suggest
the footing of your ass?

01:52.840 --> 01:55.573
this is not the ass
you're looking for.

01:57.773 --> 02:00.073
See, now you don't know
what to do.

02:04.399 --> 02:08.666
You guys, yesterday at the salon
I gave a shampoo to tina simpson.

02:08.699 --> 02:10.232
